descriptionHtml:
A community for those impacted by Type 1 Diabetes.

Together, we’re creating the largest collection of practical ideas, stories and resources for not only living with Type 1, but thriving with it.

Use the Beyond Type 1 app to:

+ Chat, message and build relationships with others impacted by Type 1 Diabetes
+ Share your story and find inspiration from members like you
+ Navigate topics surrounding Type 1 that don’t have easy or obvious answers

Members of Beyond Type 1 are connecting around topics like:

+ Being Newly Diagnosed
+ Troubleshooting Together
+ Burnout
+ Devices and T1D Tech
+ Managing Stress & Support
+ Being Parents of Young Kids with Type 1

Learn more at community.beyondtype1.org

*** Join us for a LIVE in-app World Diabetes Day celebration on Tuesday, November 14 at Noon ET! The Beyond Type 1 team will be sharing our life-saving #SeeTheSigns of diabetes campaign and talking about all the fun ways you can get involved. ***

Use the Beyond Type 1 community app to:

+ Chat, message and build relationships with others impacted by type 1 diabetes
+ Share your story and find inspiration from community members like you
+ Navigate topics surrounding T1D that don’t have easy or obvious answers
+ Get involved with Beyond Type 1 programs

Members of Beyond Type 1 are connecting around:

+ Being Newly Diagnosed
+ Troubleshooting Together
+ Burnout
+ Devices and T1D Tech
+ Managing Stress + Support
+ Being Parents of Young Kids with T1D

The Beyond Type 1 community app is supported by resources that can be found at BeyondType1.org (and in Spanish at es.BeyondType1.org).
_________

Did you know we have an app to support our friends with type 2 diabetes, too? Check out the Beyond Type 2 app!
_________

Una comunidad divertida y de apoyo para personas que viven con diabetes tipo 1. Con la mayor colección de ideas prácticas, historias y recursos para no sólo vivir con DT1, sino prosperar con ella, disponible en inglés y español.

Usa la aplicación de la comunidad Beyond Type 1 para:

+ Chatear, enviar mensajes y entablar pláticas con otras personas que viven con diabetes tipo 1
+ Compartir tu historia y encontrar inspiración de miembros de la comunidad como tú
+ Navegar por temas relacionados con la DT1 que no tienen respuestas fáciles u obvias
+Involúcrate en los programas de Beyond Type 1

Los miembros de Beyond Type 1 se conectan en torno a temas como:

+ Diagnóstico reciente
+ Solucionar problemas juntos
+ Burnout (o cansancio emocional)
+ Dispositivos y tecnología para la DT1
+ Manejo del estrés + Apoyo
+ Ser padres de niños pequeños con DT1

La aplicación de comunidad Beyond Type 1 está respaldada por recursos que se pueden encontrar en BeyondType1.org (y en español en es.BeyondType1.org).
_________
